[240.986722, "o", "\u001b[4mNICE\u001b[24m(1)                    User Commands                    \u001b[4mNICE\u001b[24m(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       nice - run a program with modified scheduling priority\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mnice \u001b[22m[\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m] [\u001b[4mCOMMAND\u001b[24m [\u001b[4mARG\u001b[24m]...]\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       Run COMMAND with an adjusted niceness, which affects process\u001b[m\r\n       scheduling.   With  no  COMMAND, print the current niceness.\u001b[m\r\n       Niceness values  range  from  \u001b[1m-20  \u001b[22m(most  favorable  to  the\u001b[m\r\n       process) to 19 (least favorable to the process).\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page nice(1) line 1 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
